{"word":"G1401 - δοῦλος - doûlos - doo'-los - Bond","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δοῦλος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">doûlos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">doo'-los</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bond</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun / பெயர்ச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"அடிமை - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"a slave, bondman, man of servile condition"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1210 - δέω - déō - deh'-o/1210\">G1210</a>; a <i>slave</i> (literally or figuratively, involuntarily or voluntarily; frequently therefore in a qualified sense of <i>subjection</i> or <i>subserviency</i>): - bond (-man), servant.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1396/1396\">G1396</a>, <a href=\"#/G1397/1397\">G1397</a>, <a href=\"#/G1398/1398\">G1398</a>, <a href=\"#/G1399/1399\">G1399</a>, <a href=\"#/G1401/1401\">G1401</a>, <a href=\"#/G1402/1402\">G1402</a>, <a href=\"#/G2615/2615\">G2615</a>, <a href=\"#/G3787/3787\">G3787</a>, <a href=\"#/G4889/4889\">G4889</a>"}]}